parameters.name: Create
parameters.description: Specifies whether to create the log shipping job.

parameters.name: DBClusterId
parameters.description:
The cluster ID.

>  You can call the [DescribeDBClusters](~~129857~~) operation to query the IDs of all AnalyticDB for MySQL Data Warehouse Edition clusters within a region.

parameters.name: DeliverName
parameters.description: The name of the log shipping job.

parameters.name: Description
parameters.description: The description of the log shipping job.

parameters.name: FilterDirtyData
parameters.description:
Specifies whether to filter dirty data.

Valid values:

*   true
*   false

parameters.name: Password
parameters.description: The password of the database account.

parameters.name: ProjectName
parameters.description: The name of the Simple Log Service project.

parameters.name: Provider
parameters.description: The channel of the log shipping job.

parameters.name: UserName
parameters.description: The name of the database account.
